{"tid":2330622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今日上庭 無懼無畏  王宗堯：將微小力量集合一齊","createTime":"2020-12-18T07:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T07:51:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2af52baefdf9b640df50b6d498a2c39da9829f50","tid":2330622,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:25:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201218/3Y2FL7JR2JEMDBVO3FHEDPKKJE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201218%2F3Y2FL7JR2JEMDBVO3FHEDPKKJE%2F&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=e715af47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201218%2F3Y2FL7JR2JEMDBVO3FHEDPKKJE%2F&h=f93d88c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201218/3Y2FL7JR2JEMDBVO3FHEDPKKJE/</a><br />\n<br />\n今日上庭 無懼無畏 <br />\n王宗堯：將微小力量集合一齊<br />\n<br />\n王宗堯今日再就涉闖立法會案應訊，面對過百萬元律師費，日前他公開懇請得到「懲罰」，即獲各方支持。《蘋果》也邀請他主持節目《王探黃》，搜探全港黃店，昨晚首集，王宗堯入將軍澳《蘋果》大樓打卡，雖然面對難關，但他依然無畏無懼：「香港人係熱心嘅，所以我都要做佢哋一分子，要將微小嘅力量集合埋一齊。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：阿澤app如期上架 越洋主持<br />\n<br />\n現年42歲的王宗堯去年7.1參加反送中遊行，其間示威者一度闖入立法會，警方去年拘控多人，9月時王宗堯被控「進入或逗留在會議廳範圍」，今年6月律政司改控更嚴重的「暴動罪」，最高刑期可判監10年，他今日要再到西九龍裁判署上庭。面對應付龐大律師費，王宗堯日前在網上求大家「懲罰」，給他工作機會。《蘋果》也邀請王宗堯主持新節目《王探黃》，由他帶大家搜探全港黃店。節目由昨晚開始，每周四晚上10時30分在果燃台和蘋果YouTube播出。昨晚首集，王宗堯就選擇入將軍澳工業邨《蘋果日報》打卡，他甫進大堂見到聖誕樹，即擔心還柙中的黎智英：「就嚟聖誕，希望黎生安好。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OaixdbWYp4qQ8BdYJaHHLT1FHRE=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EWX7W74ZJZHYVDUNRZQNVPYFGU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOaixdbWYp4qQ8BdYJaHHLT1FHRE%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEWX7W74ZJZHYVDUNRZQNVPYFGU.jpg&h=6f473a21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■王宗堯年中被改控暴動罪，今早上庭。<br />\n<br />\n王宗堯在主播汶汶陪伴下，洗樓式逐層探秘，他到一樓《9點半蘋果新聞報道》的直播室參觀，更坐上主播位嘗試報道新聞，依稿讀出李偲嫣死訊，之後他上二樓採訪部探記者朋友，再去取回訂購的寫上「Uncovering The Truth Confronting Injustice」（用真相對抗不義）的白色tee，王宗堯笑言一串長英文字會「嚇窒」某些人：「有啲人唔識咁多英文字就唔會搞你。」然後他上五樓canteen休息，不少同事上前為他打氣，還請他吃糯米糍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CnnJAlp63NepDhVX3HW0DM9HDZw=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2ZU6BHXRU5FQVB34EMLF6RJCFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCnnJAlp63NepDhVX3HW0DM9HDZw%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2ZU6BHXRU5FQVB34EMLF6RJCFA.jpg&h=bd0db9ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■小店「Belongs to J」與王宗堯前晚宣佈推出聯乘刺繡扣針，現正預售中，更會送出王宗堯簽名postcard。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5xnpX7ZIZbaS0Y9FHM-x_Rxv_7I=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EIBSZPAGCZB3NL376NKHZKTKFQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5xnpX7ZIZbaS0Y9FHM-x_Rxv_7I%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEIBSZPAGCZB3NL376NKHZKTKFQ.jpg&h=ce668042&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■王宗堯告急後，獲黃店「咖啡公義」邀約代言，大前晚親自為產品簽名。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oQdzec2euVFwtB54S5phPII41mQ=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CWKDFKTLY5HGFEUEXGG6YGJMDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoQdzec2euVFwtB54S5phPII41mQ%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCWKDFKTLY5HGFEUEXGG6YGJMDA.jpg&h=7c1b1250&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■王宗堯前日到譚文豪開設的餐廳「一日三餐」做一日店長，袋五位數酬勞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qEgqGL5ORrNPlN1YWpauxrrtTqU=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TWJVH6CGNJGP3DFKRQKOXANH2E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqEgqGL5ORrNPlN1YWpauxrrtTqU%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTWJVH6CGNJGP3DFKRQKOXANH2E.jpg&h=4fea1320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■渣哥（右）前日宣佈王宗堯明日會到旗下茶餐廳做一日代言人，薪酬10萬元。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最怕清晨門鈴聲<br />\n<br />\n拍攝後，王宗堯接受訪問，提到今日再踏入法院，近日連番出現法官不允被告保釋，問到他可有作出最壞打算，他說：「有嘅，我係平常心。」他又指現在特別害怕清晨的門鈴聲：「有過一次經驗（指去年被補），睇住新聞多少都有啲同感。」即使前面還有重重難關，王宗堯堅持無畏無懼：「我哋有困難時間，香港人係熱心嘅，所以我都要做佢哋一分子，要將微小嘅力量集合埋一齊。」提到家人，王宗堯指雖然少談政治，但有需要時也會傾吓：「屋企始終係自己最強後盾，你會喺嗰度攞到好多關心。自己去到呢個年紀，屋企人開始老，我要做好自己，唔好令佢哋擔心，要令屋企人安心。」<br />\n<br />\n再踏入《蘋果》大樓，王宗堯直言有回家的感覺：「同事氣氛好好，我每次入嚟都好開心，細個未入娛圈，對傳媒呢行有幻想、有憧憬，好想有機會入去睇吓！」他續說：「我好多謝《蘋果》一路好照顧我，珍惜見到大家都仲喺度，經歷過去年（反送中運動）同今年8月（200警搜《蘋果》大樓）事件，好開心你哋未放棄。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RrFT5fA8DLq0RaBt7zmpWEXo7H4=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UNZVE24DXBD5VHV3JH6F7P4MGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRrFT5fA8DLq0RaBt7zmpWEXo7H4%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUNZVE24DXBD5VHV3JH6F7P4MGY.jpg&h=936b4d42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■王宗堯昨日探《蘋果》，到直播室試做主播。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4poe_DdTQXFRA-a5c202BKOdVmM=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5EUHW7AFWREBFBENU3PU356MJA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4poe_DdTQXFRA-a5c202BKOdVmM%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5EUHW7AFWREBFBENU3PU356MJA.jpg&h=430cc832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■王宗堯領取印有英文「用真相對抗不義」的T恤，笑說長長的英文可以「嚇窒」某些人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做代言任「股東」<br />\n<br />\n王宗堯大前日告急後，不少黃店即採取行動，王宗堯明日會在銅鑼灣的「大渣哥茶記」做一日代言人，渣哥表示：「不扣除任何成本，營業額10萬。」並指若然不夠10萬，由渣哥團隊包底。另外，有商舖直接在王宗堯的網頁上邀請，食店「Try My Bread」寫道：「誠聘王宗堯到小店兼職股東三小時（當日營業額三成）。」王宗堯也回覆多謝，指要安排工作時間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uFaTyTYiVeUDich9FBv0l2F0cX0=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/55W77CNHEBBFXATUI623RQZBYI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuFaTyTYiVeUDich9FBv0l2F0cX0%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F55W77CNHEBBFXATUI623RQZBYI.jpg&h=53d85309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《蘋果》同事為王宗堯打氣，還貼心送上糯米糍。"},{"pid":"5bea8578fba262b4f345c8c538d78f0e8c769ec0","tid":2330622,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:25:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c88790497faf7e99711af5d3566558a34f9198","tid":2330622,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:28:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f65d8c1f426fc79cf2021cde6b23b658610ca38","tid":2330622,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:29:06.000Z","msg":"王宗堯受「懲罰」主持新節目《王探黃》 <br />\n搜探全港黃店今入《蘋果》踩場 <br />\n撐同路人計劃 自由定價支持 <br />\n#Appledaily #蘋果日報 #王宗堯 #黃店<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lnxVU_RVdeM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlnxVU_RVdeM&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=ddd829e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lnxVU_RVdeM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果動新聞 HK Apple Daily<br />\n1.76M subscribers<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》邀請了王宗堯主持新節目《王探黃》，顧名思義，由金黃的王宗堯帶大家搜探全港黃店，介紹好玩、好吃、好買兼好打卡的地方。王宗堯將會由今日開始，每周出動探一間黃店，雖然王宗堯明天要出庭應訊，心情複雜，但今日他堅持繼續工作，首集就帶觀眾深入黃媒《蘋果日報》。<br />\n<br />\n轉到「果燃台」收看本節目 以自由定價撐同路人  <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3gZmONr\" data-s